## Educational Assistance

Programs to help learners understand basic programming concepts interactively.

## Features

- Print messages  
- Variables & data types  
- If statements  
- Loops  
- Functions

## Usage

1. Clone the repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/M-web186/educational-assistance.git
   cd educational-assistance
Run the script:
bash
python "programming basics"
Follow the prompts to learn programming basics.

## Example Output
Code
